For someone who frequently flies for work, this is shocking:

Four crucial bolts were apparently not installed on the Boeing 737 Max 9 jet that lost a door panel in mid-flight last month, federal investigators said in a report.

The bolts appeared to be missing when the brand new jet left the Boeing factory. https://cbsn.ws/487xNNF
